## VOID (9)

```
∅ compulsion              -.85 | forced "play" is not play (C1 violation)
∅ consent_breach          -.82 | using others as pieces without mutual entry (C1,C2,C5)
∅ infinite_stakes         -.82 | when failure destroys the player, play collapses (C2 violation)
∅ frame_trap              -.80 | play-frame cannot be exited (C5 negation)
∅ unconscious_pretense    -.78 | believing the mask is the face, unknowingly (C3 violation)
∅ manipulative_play       -.75 | using play-frame to exploit/control others (C1,C5)
∅ unrecognized_play       -.72 | play no one can see as play has no exit (C5 violation)
∅ mere_escapism           -.68 | play that denies return; flight not exploration
∅ cruelty_as_play         -.65 | Victor's "hellish sport"; violates C2 for the other
```

